{"tid":341654,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(刀具)想買把柳刃返黎開魚","createTime":"2017-07-31T03:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T04:26:59.000Z","uid":61295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67494bd9e8f473ef08db095fc7b3ae5a7d50458d","tid":341654,"uid":61295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:26:14.000Z","msg":"小弟打算訂一條原條刺身三文魚返黎自己開(第一次開魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n屎忽痕想買返把柳刃返黎片魚生<br />\n唔洗太貴(筆直$500)，因為我唔係專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我上網睇過下，睇中左呢吧<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/112257_85438863c2714291665405e5dfe82fcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F112257_85438863c2714291665405e5dfe82fcb.jpg&h=cef9c8d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貝印 關孫六 柳刃 240mm<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知唔知呢把野好唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者有無其他選擇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901ce940d83dc7fa7e18c9f549d90043b19ec332","tid":341654,"uid":87687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:51:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟打算訂一條原條刺身三文魚返黎自己開(第一次開魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n屎忽痕想買返把柳刃返黎片魚生<br />\n唔洗太貴(筆直$500)，因為我唔係專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我上網睇過下，睇中左呢吧<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/112257_85438863c2714291665405e5dfe82fcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F112257_85438863c2714291665405e5dfe82fcb.jpg&h=cef9c8d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貝印 關孫六 柳刃 240mm<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知唔知呢把野好唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者有無其他選擇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquo