lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都有錯"},{"pid":"5940f7f313e8daadcc278e66b3a77e050458b552","tid":341654,"uid":87687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該巴打<br />\n幾時交收，你係邊到翻工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntg 係@alex118 ,<br />\n不是同一把，我比相你睇下0岩唔0岩先"},{"pid":"36736af7a86b49663766ef2431b70f0cebc50b93","tid":341654,"uid":101550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係勁既 菜刀都夠</blockquote><br />\n咪寫左第一次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工欲善其事啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都有錯</blockquote><br />\n呢啲魚生刀好煩要成磨<br />\n好易鈍<br />\n你唔介意就冇問題"},{"pid":"8b621ce2a3c244942bcb3e1a1a078a63e5d5c0c6","tid":341654,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係勁既 菜刀都夠</blockquote><br />\n咪寫左第一次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工欲善其事啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都有錯</blockquote><br />\n呢啲魚生刀好煩要成磨<br />\n好易鈍<br />\n你唔介意就冇問題</blockquote><br />\n要利一定要磨架啦"},{"pid":"4223daba0f63e7cff430fc72c332833dc01f04cd","tid":341654,"uid":61295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係勁既 菜刀都夠</blockquote><br />\n咪寫左第一次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工欲善其事啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都有錯</blockquote><br />\n呢啲魚生刀好煩要成磨<br />\n好易鈍<br />\n你唔介意就冇問題</blockquote><br />\n要利一定要磨架啦</blockquote><br />\n遲啲去上海街買磨刀石<br />\n400/1000雙面係咪夠洗夠用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋係咪最簡單平磨就ok？<br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bbdbe561870fd7ed2afe2e91a39596eb02e978","tid":341654,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係勁既 菜刀都夠</blockquote><br />\n咪寫左第一次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工欲善其事啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都有錯</blockquote><br />\n呢啲魚生刀好煩要成磨<br />\n好易鈍<br />\n你唔介意就冇問題</blockquote><br />\n要利一定要磨架啦</blockquote><br />\n遲啲去上海街買磨刀石<br />\n400/1000雙面係咪夠洗夠用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋係咪最簡單平磨就ok？<br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n400 / 1000 磿唔到鏡面刃口，不過開魚洗唔洗鏡面刃口我就唔知了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a277a94f93b70ac1d362b5cf2260de02d5615bf0","tid":341654,"uid":87687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係勁既 菜刀都夠</blockquote><br />\n咪寫左第一次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工欲善其事啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都有錯</blockquote><br />\n呢啲魚生刀好煩要成磨<br />\n好易鈍<br />\n你唔介意就冇問題</blockquote><br />\n要利一定要磨架啦</blockquote><br />\n遲啲去上海街買磨刀石<br />\n400/1000雙面係咪夠洗夠用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋係咪最簡單平磨就ok？<br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新刀唔係用咁粗的。上山用既刀，預佢成日崩口捲口，係&ldquo;鈍(切唔到紙)&rdquo;同&ldquo;ok利(切紙唔順)&rdquo;之間來回先係400/1000。廚房可以用3000/8000。因為你係keep 住佢&ldquo;利&rdquo;同&ldquo;好Ｌ利&rdquo;之間來回。太粗唔work 架。<br />\n<br />\n另一個選擇係每次用前後直接strope, 齋皮帶或皮帶加compound. 新刀其實呢個做法最間單實際。不過似乎無廚師用呢個方法。唔知咩原因。求指導。"},{"pid":"440937d14be3f009f2d8b33e6dacf2d547a5310a","tid":341654,"uid":101550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係勁既 菜刀都夠</blockquote><br />\n咪寫左第一次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工欲善其事啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都有錯</blockquote><br />\n呢啲魚生刀好煩要成磨<br />\n好易鈍<br />\n你唔介意就冇問題</blockquote><br />\n要利一定要磨架啦</blockquote><br />\n我嘅意思係要成日磨<br />\n日本刀或者佢個磨刀方法係另把刀做到極致鋒利<br />\n但耐用度就低過西式廚房刀或者中菜刀<br />\n如果要keep住個鋒利度就要成日磨"},{"pid":"88bd427cfada7b5575a9b945506a4233c808215d","tid":341654,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"淘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39017722fc9ed2232833fe21bbc63c02d12928db","tid":341654,"uid":61295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係勁既 菜刀都夠</blockquote><br />\n咪寫左第一次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工欲善其事啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都有錯</blockquote><br />\n呢啲魚生刀好煩要成磨<br />\n好易鈍<br />\n你唔介意就冇問題</blockquote><br />\n要利一定要磨架啦</blockquote><br />\n遲啲去上海街買磨刀石<br />\n400/1000雙面係咪夠洗夠用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋係咪最簡單平磨就ok？<br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新刀唔係用咁粗的。上山用既刀，預佢成日崩口捲口，係&ldquo;鈍(切唔到紙)&rdquo;同&ldquo;ok利(切紙唔順)&rdquo;之間來回先係400/1000。廚房可以用3000/8000。因為你係keep 住佢&ldquo;利&rdquo;同&ldquo;好Ｌ利&rdquo;之間來回。太粗唔work 架。<br />\n<br />\n另一個選擇係每次用前後直接strope, 齋皮帶或皮帶加compound. 新刀其實呢個做法最間單實際。不過似乎無廚師用呢個方法。唔知咩原因。求指導。</blockquote><br />\n長知識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心多謝指教"},{"pid":"0b089c3f534c51bbf0de49c12f7